{"title":"Pivot TIG up 2021 Point steel hardtail DJ Bike for frequent flyers w/ adjustable stays","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/03/23/pivot-tig-up-2021-point-steel-hardtail-dj-bike-for-frequent-flyers-w-adjustable-stays/","date":1616501943000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>Pivot Cycles have reintroduced the steel frame Point dirt jump bike for 2021, with adjustable rear dropouts and a complete geometry refresh. Don’t worry, there is no <em>actual</em> Pivot Point. It’s still a hardtail running a 26″ wheelset. Let’s take a closer look at this reinvention of a modern classic ridden to fame by Aaron Chase, Elliot Jackson and Kyle Strait.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23074535/pivot-point-steel-hardtail-mtb-dirt-jumper-park-bike.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23074535/pivot-point-steel-hardtail-mtb-dirt-jumper-park-bike.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x323/rscb8/ng:webp/ngcb8\" alt=\"pivot point dj bike steel frame hardtailmtb\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23074535/pivot-point-steel-hardtail-mtb-dirt-jumper-park-bike.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x323/rscb8/ng:webp/ngcb8\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23074535/pivot-point-steel-hardtail-mtb-dirt-jumper-park-bike.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23074535/pivot-point-steel-hardtail-mtb-dirt-jumper-park-bike-297x198.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23074535/pivot-point-steel-hardtail-mtb-dirt-jumper-park-bike-800x533.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23074535/pivot-point-steel-hardtail-mtb-dirt-jumper-park-bike-120x80.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23074535/pivot-point-steel-hardtail-mtb-dirt-jumper-park-bike-768x512.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23074535/pivot-point-steel-hardtail-mtb-dirt-jumper-park-bike-696x464.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23074535/pivot-point-steel-hardtail-mtb-dirt-jumper-park-bike-1068x712.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23074535/pivot-point-steel-hardtail-mtb-dirt-jumper-park-bike-630x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 630w\" ezoid=\"0.5794000022460106\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23074535/pivot-point-steel-hardtail-mtb-dirt-jumper-park-bike.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23074535/pivot-point-steel-hardtail-mtb-dirt-jumper-park-bike-297x198.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23074535/pivot-point-steel-hardtail-mtb-dirt-jumper-park-bike-800x533.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23074535/pivot-point-steel-hardtail-mtb-dirt-jumper-park-bike-120x80.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23074535/pivot-point-steel-hardtail-mtb-dirt-jumper-park-bike-768x512.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23074535/pivot-point-steel-hardtail-mtb-dirt-jumper-park-bike-696x464.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23074535/pivot-point-steel-hardtail-mtb-dirt-jumper-park-bike-1068x712.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23074535/pivot-point-steel-hardtail-mtb-dirt-jumper-park-bike-630x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 630w\"></a></p><p>The 2021 Pivot Point dirt jump bike gets a TIG-welded double-butted 4130 chromoly steel frame requiring just one gusset at the headtube-downtube interface. The Point gets a geometry refresh for this model year. Still rolling on 26″ wheels, we see a slightly steeper head tube angle of 68.5° and a steeper seat tube angle of 72°.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23080107/2021-pivot-point-100mm-fork-dj-bike-steel-frame.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23080107/2021-pivot-point-100mm-fork-dj-bike-steel-frame.jpg\" alt=\"2021 pivot point hardtail mtb 100mm fork dirtjump bike dj park riding\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23080107/2021-pivot-point-100mm-fork-dj-bike-steel-frame.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23080107/2021-pivot-point-100mm-fork-dj-bike-steel-frame.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23080107/2021-pivot-point-100mm-fork-dj-bike-steel-frame-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23080107/2021-pivot-point-100mm-fork-dj-bike-steel-frame-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23080107/2021-pivot-point-100mm-fork-dj-bike-steel-frame-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23080107/2021-pivot-point-100mm-fork-dj-bike-steel-frame-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23080107/2021-pivot-point-100mm-fork-dj-bike-steel-frame-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23080107/2021-pivot-point-100mm-fork-dj-bike-steel-frame-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23080107/2021-pivot-point-100mm-fork-dj-bike-steel-frame-630x420.jpg 630w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23080107/2021-pivot-point-100mm-fork-dj-bike-steel-frame.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23080107/2021-pivot-point-100mm-fork-dj-bike-steel-frame-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23080107/2021-pivot-point-100mm-fork-dj-bike-steel-frame-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23080107/2021-pivot-point-100mm-fork-dj-bike-steel-frame-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23080107/2021-pivot-point-100mm-fork-dj-bike-steel-frame-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23080107/2021-pivot-point-100mm-fork-dj-bike-steel-frame-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23080107/2021-pivot-point-100mm-fork-dj-bike-steel-frame-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23080107/2021-pivot-point-100mm-fork-dj-bike-steel-frame-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>This steel dirt jump bike is designed around a 100mm fork. It has a reach of 425.8mm, meant to work with a 35mm stem. It gets a stout, tapered head tube measuring up at 110mm.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23075913/2021-pivot-point-single-speed-configuration.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23075913/2021-pivot-point-single-speed-configuration.jpg\" alt=\"2021 pivot point steel dirt jump bike adjustable rear dropouts chainstay length singles peed or derailleur\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23075913/2021-pivot-point-single-speed-configuration.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23075913/2021-pivot-point-single-speed-configuration.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23075913/2021-pivot-point-single-speed-configuration-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23075913/2021-pivot-point-single-speed-configuration-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23075913/2021-pivot-point-single-speed-configuration-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23075913/2021-pivot-point-single-speed-configuration-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23075913/2021-pivot-point-single-speed-configuration-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23075913/2021-pivot-point-single-speed-configuration-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23075913/2021-pivot-point-single-speed-configuration-630x420.jpg 630w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23075913/2021-pivot-point-single-speed-configuration.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23075913/2021-pivot-point-single-speed-configuration-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23075913/2021-pivot-point-single-speed-configuration-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23075913/2021-pivot-point-single-speed-configuration-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23075913/2021-pivot-point-single-speed-configuration-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23075913/2021-pivot-point-single-speed-configuration-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23075913/2021-pivot-point-single-speed-configuration-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23075913/2021-pivot-point-single-speed-configuration-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>Gone are the DMR SwopOut system dropouts seen on its <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2015/03/24/pivot-points-to-new-dj-color-travels-to-queenstown-with-eliot-jackson/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">predecessor</a>, replaced by adjustable ones that allow the rider to tune chainstay length from 385mm to 400mm. As the bike is only available in one size, this is likely a feature that most riders will make use of. Riders can also choose between running a rear derailleur or opting to set the Pivot Point up as a single speed.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23074513/2021-pivot-point-back-flip-steel-hardtail-dirt-jump-bike.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23074513/2021-pivot-point-back-flip-steel-hardtail-dirt-jump-bike.jpg\" alt=\"backfliping 2021 pivot point steel dirt jump bike\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23074513/2021-pivot-point-back-flip-steel-hardtail-dirt-jump-bike.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23074513/2021-pivot-point-back-flip-steel-hardtail-dirt-jump-bike.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23074513/2021-pivot-point-back-flip-steel-hardtail-dirt-jump-bike-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23074513/2021-pivot-point-back-flip-steel-hardtail-dirt-jump-bike-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23074513/2021-pivot-point-back-flip-steel-hardtail-dirt-jump-bike-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23074513/2021-pivot-point-back-flip-steel-hardtail-dirt-jump-bike-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23074513/2021-pivot-point-back-flip-steel-hardtail-dirt-jump-bike-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23074513/2021-pivot-point-back-flip-steel-hardtail-dirt-jump-bike-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23074513/2021-pivot-point-back-flip-steel-hardtail-dirt-jump-bike-630x420.jpg 630w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23074513/2021-pivot-point-back-flip-steel-hardtail-dirt-jump-bike.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23074513/2021-pivot-point-back-flip-steel-hardtail-dirt-jump-bike-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23074513/2021-pivot-point-back-flip-steel-hardtail-dirt-jump-bike-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23074513/2021-pivot-point-back-flip-steel-hardtail-dirt-jump-bike-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23074513/2021-pivot-point-back-flip-steel-hardtail-dirt-jump-bike-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23074513/2021-pivot-point-back-flip-steel-hardtail-dirt-jump-bike-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23074513/2021-pivot-point-back-flip-steel-hardtail-dirt-jump-bike-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/23074513/2021-pivot-point-back-flip-steel-hardtail-dirt-jump-bik